///

/// GATE_OR

@node GATE_OR
@title "OR"


OR

Shortcut: o


The output is HIGH when at least one of the inputs  is HIGH.


You can choose the number of inputs (2, 3 or 5) in the
menu or the "basic gates"-window.

Click on the gate to replace it with @{"AND" link GATE_AND}, @{"NAND" link GATE_NAND}, @{"NOR" link GATE_NOR}, @{"XOR" link GATE_XOR}.




      A | B | Q
     ---+---+---
      0 | 0 | 0         A - input 1
      0 | 1 | 1         B - input 2
      1 | 0 | 1         Q - output
      1 | 1 | 1



   @{" Show Gate    " system "execute gfx/Show gfx/OR.iff"}
   @{" Show diagram " system "execute gfx/Show gfx/OR_diagram.iff"}



