///

/// GATE_NOT

@node GATE_NOT
@title "NOT"


NOT

Shortcut: n


The output is an inverted input.
If input is LOW, output is HIGH.
If input is HIGH, output is LOW.




      A | Q
     ---+---
      0 | 1          A - input
      1 | 0          Q - output




   @{" Show Gate    " system "execute gfx/Show gfx/NOT.iff"}
   @{" Show diagram " system "execute gfx/Show gfx/NOT_diagram.iff"}



