///

/// GATE_JKMSFF

@node GATE_JKMSFF
@title "JKMS FlipFlop"


JKMS FlipFlop

JK-Master-Slave FlipFlop

J = Set
K = Reset
C = Clock
Q = Output
/Q= inverted Output

This type of FlipFlop consists internally of two @{"JK-FlipFlops" link GATE_JKFF}.
The output is only changed when clock jumps from HIGH to LOW.


   @{" Show Gate    " system "execute gfx/Show gfx/JKMSFF.iff"}
   @{" Show diagram " system "execute gfx/Show gfx/JKMSFF_diagram.iff"}



