@node GATE_JKMSRSFF
@title "JKMS FlipFlop (S/R)"


JKMS FlipFlop (S/R)

JK-Master-Slave FlipFlop with Set/Reset


This is the same as @{"JKMS-FlipFlop" link GATE_JKMSFF}, but it
has special inputs to set and reset the output independent from
the J, K and CLK inputs.

This can be used for example with counters that reset after the
10th impulse.

