   |             |
   |_____________|
   +--------------------------------------->
                                          t
   ^
  S|
   |                          ____
   |                         |    |
   |                         |    |
   |_________________________|    |_____
   +--------------------------------------->
                                          t
   ^
  R|
   |                             ____
   |                            |    |
   |                            |    |
   |____________________________|    |__
   +--------------------------------------->
                                          t

   ^
  Q|
   |            _____         __
   |           |     |       |  |
   |           |     |       |  |
   |___________|     |_______|  |_______
   +--------------------------------------->
                                          t
   ^
 /Q|
   |___________       _______    _______
   |           |     |       |  |
   |           |     |       |  |
   |           |_____|       |__|
